# AuraTxt Profile Generator — AI Prompt

## How to use this file

1. Copy everything below the line "── Paste to AI chat ──"
2. Paste it into any AI chat (Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini, DeepSeek …)
3. At the very end, add your model's API call template (Python / curl / JSON)
4. Copy the JSON the AI returns → save as `profiles/<id>.json`
5. Validate:  `auracfg profile --validate profiles/<id>.json`
6. Reload:    `auracfg profile --reload`  (or restart auracfg)

